}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "M01-R5506-E10" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
Per the FCC label, the default SSID is '''ZyXEL'''.
The power adapter included with the device is a '''DVE''' DSA-12G-12 FUS 120120 (12V, 1A).
